 and weaknesses.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aBanks and bankingxGreat Britain. 0aBanks and bankingxIslamic countries. 0aBanks and bankingxReligious aspectsxIslam. 0aBanks and bankingzGreat Britain. 0aBanks and bankingzIslamic countries. 0aConflict of lawszGreat Britain. 0aFinance (Islamic law). 0aFinancial services industryzGreat Britain. 0aIslamic lawzGreat Britain. 4aIslamic Studies. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Accounting / Financial.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEdinburgh University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2013-2000z978311078046840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978074864487240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780748644872423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780748644872/original  a978-3-11-078046-8  Edinburgh University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2013-2000c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LAEC  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK